{"tid":367971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"牛屎佬賺得多過賣料","createTime":"2017-08-21T07:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T07:46:55.000Z","uid":1373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5cbfff94fadc00461f3fbc19d8cb628b2d72b60","tid":367971,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"一開始派錢吸引手足 大家衝哂去俾馬會ac佢<br />\n之後又以打擊賣料狗為名 手足當佢神咁拜<br />\n但有又無交代點解刀仔個啲咁順利退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其後開個垃圾line gp 要俾ig佢先可以入<br />\n但唔用個line gp 用返tg gp 攞晒大家啲資料<br />\n最近仲問人拎埋電話 又賣廣告 <br />\n今日又話派40-80個人 又可以拎一堆資料起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係賣廣告同賣資料已經好和味了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c72d6e7bd2e0cba36e5fdfb1042928af89a5bf","tid":367971,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/155705_aacdabfcd3deefc7b1d43fdfc1008a52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F155705_aacdabfcd3deefc7b1d43fdfc1008a52.jpg&h=99b56660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辛苦你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbc81a8ea0c34fcb876a548932b564e7f780a59","tid":367971,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/160503_1f7c064053f3a3aab2dd3c38fa1bde11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F160503_1f7c064053f3a3aab2dd3c38fa1bde11.jpg&h=042a3d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n角球一日大一日細"},{"pid":"4bff225e5c12dee89271686de14d86dd34fdedc7","tid":367971,"uid":1373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/160712_039b755c05de46ba1ddcc19